commit.message: Updated to request People and display the output in a TextArea.

Updated LifeScopeClient.cs in top-level Assets to use token broker
backend and retrieve user ID.

Updated access code to be an 8-digit alphanumeric string.
/complete now checks if a session with that code exists and only uses
an unused code.

Removed passing the client_id on create_session since we already have
that as an environment variable.
Changed query parameter 'scope' to 'scopes'.

Added 'created' field to auth_sessions with default value of now.
create_session now removes all sessions older than five minutes to
prevent reuse.

exchange_code does not get session_id from the cookie since it will
likely be called from a Unity session that doesn't have the cookie.
We're relying on the code being unique and quickly erased after use.
Added lambda function for acquiring and exchanging OAuth tokens.
Added ML code login screen fixes.
auth, token access, refresh token request/response
